TRUST BOND INTEGRATION

Trust bonds, as implemented in the Kingdom Framework, represent
cryptographic consent between Natural Persons. This license does not
supersede trust bond obligations; it provides the legal layer underlying
them. A Sovereign Operator who has issued trust bonds to other persons
remains the Sovereign Operator for purposes of this license.

Receiving a trust bond from another kingdom does not grant that kingdom
authority over your Kingdom for licensing purposes. Each Kingdom has one
Sovereign Operator.

